name: Sasuke vs. Commander
overview:
Sasuke vs Commander (サスケＶＳコマンダー) is a shooting gallery arcade game developed by Shin Nihon Kikaku. It was released sometime in 1980, making it one of the many titles released before the Neo Geo system.
Taking place in the city of Kyoto, Sasuke fights against commanders who repel him with magics such as Henshin, Bushin, Kaen and Hiryuken.
